  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TCP报文结构的packet图，从0到255位，按位来展示各个字段。开头应该是Source Port和Destination Port，各占16位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，0-15位是Source Port，16-31位是Destination Port，对吗？然后接下来是Sequence Number？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。Sequence Number和Acknowledgment Number各占32位，所以32-63是Sequence Number，64-95是Acknowledgment Number。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，前面四个字段已经画好了。接下来96-99位是Data Offset，100-105是Reserved，然后六个标志位：URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN各占一位，从106到111。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来112-127位是Window字段，然后128-143是Checksum，144-159是Urgent Pointer。这里要注意Window和Urgent Pointer的区别。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。最后两个部分应该是Options and Padding，还有Data对吧？Options的长度是可变的，Data也是可变长度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options and Padding",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。160-191位给Options and Padding，192-255位是Data。不过要在括号里注明variable length，说明Data长度是可变的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Options and Padding",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个TCP报文结构从0到255位全部画好，标题设为\"TCP Packet\"，所有字段包括六个标志位、Window、Urgent Pointer以及Options and Padding和可变长度的Data都按位标注清楚了。",
